text.data-name: Server Insights is a new experimental feature from Discord that gives you visibility into how your server is doing. Is it healthy? Are people talking? What's your retention look like? These are all questions that were hard or impossible to answer before.
text.tspan: Server Insights is a new experimental feature from Discord that gives you visibility into how
your server is doing. Is it healthy? Are people talking? What's your retention look like?
These are all questions that were hard or impossible to answer before.
Now, they're easy, and come in pretty charts!

text.data-name: Server Insights is an alpha feature, so there may be bugs!
Want to dive deeper? See more detailed analytics about your server in the Developer Portal!
